Airandou has postet a new Doujin for 2 days :D

Skimmed the previews on DLsite before it got uploaded so it wasn’t expect anything amazing. Some solid stories and art but some of the best (hayake, Maeshima Ryo, and that one set at the school sex club mostly) got cut short IMO. Also wtf Maeshima Ryo decided they wanted to make an Ichihaya ending, I can truly say I never thought they’d do something like this, at least not in LO; can’t say I’m a fan either tbh. Anyway,  an average 5-6, I need to review the stories a couple more times before I can definitively say or not. Hope y’all can enjoy at least 1-2 of the stories, see y’all next month.

For some reason I was very anxious for this month, I was more disappointed than usual, but overall I'm feeling its another 4/10, I liked some but my expectations were too high, maybe its a 5/10. Anyways enjoy it oniichans EHEHE
